radiographic_examinations.findings: Occlusion of the internal carotid arteries distal to the origin of the ophthalmic artery with moyamoya vessels and a leptomeningeal/transdural anastomosis.
Right frontal cortical infarct and several bilateral subcortical infarcts.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: New brain infarctions in the right middle cerebral artery territory observed at a later date.
